{"tid":846324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友鐘意睇大陸劇","createTime":"2018-10-03T10:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T10:58:09.000Z","uid":42753,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"940d0186f76eb9f2697da7832598bfd54e7105ae","tid":846324,"uid":42753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"之前套延禧日播夜播，仲要睇大陸版<br />\n宜家做完又開第二套睇 仲要都係古裝劇<br />\n古裝劇..咩人先鐘意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我喺佢隔黎成日聽到蝗語對白真係好撚煩<br />\n同佢講呢啲係c奶先會睇 (我地90後<br />\n我呀媽都唔睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後又學埋啲對白定喺道唱大戲 平日喺耳邊噏幾句 <br />\n屌真係好撚銀耳 我同佢講你唔好再喺我耳邊普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以邊個話港女一定崇洋崇韓..."},{"pid":"5143ac944596660c1699b6f6cc458fd86df2fbdf","tid":846324,"uid":177152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"1a11b62a257d0068449a8de283e9568ef3133423","tid":846324,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"f7d932c7ee96bb1b8983cc4fc2345511e42edcfc","tid":846324,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"中出即飛, 我幫你埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}